元設計
* main
  - original
    ./src/main -- logic
    ./src/main/static/* -- static
  - development
    ./build/main -- logic 
    ./build/main/main.js -- package.json/main
    ./build/main -- base (default)
    ./build/main/static/* -- static
  - deployment
    ./build/main -- logic 
    ./build/main/main.js -- package.json/main
    ./ -- base
    ./static/* -- static
* renderer
  - original
    ./src/renderer -- logic
    ./public/* -- static
  - development
    ./build/renderer -- logic
    ./build/renderer/index.html -- dev-server root is ./build/renderer
    http://localhost:port/ -- src/main/main.ts
    http://localhost:port/* -- static
  - deployment
    ./renderer -- logic
    ./renderer/* -- static

Solution -- main側でも、./publicをstatic相当にする
* main
  - original
    ./public/* -- static
  - development
    ./build/main/public/* -- static
  - deployment
    ./public/* -- static